text: The Parade () is a 2011 Serbian Slovenian Croatian French Macedonian British comedy-drama movie directed by Srđan Dragojević and starring Nikola Kojo, Miloš Samolov, Goran Jevtić, Hristina Popović, Dejan Aćimović, Toni Mihajlovski, Goran Navojec, Mira Stupica, Relja Popović, Nataša Marković. == Other websites == * Category:2011 comedy-drama movies Category:2011 LGBT movies Category:Serbian movies Category:Slovenian movies Category:Croatian movies Category:French comedy movies Category:French drama movies Category:French LGBT movies Category:Macedonian movies Category:British comedy-drama movies Category:British LGBT movies
